margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131110765.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Joan Kroc's monumental donation, recognized by Guinness World Records, funded the construction of numerous community centers across the US. These Kroc Centers offer vital recreational, educational, and social services, becoming hubs for community life and fostering social interaction. The legacy ensures sustainable operation, making her gift a tangible and lasting impact on countless lives.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-surprising-reason-joan-krocs-record-breaking-salvation-army-gift-still-changes-lives-today/articleshow/131110765.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-surprising-reason-joan-krocs-record-breaking-salvation-army-gift-still-changes-lives-today/articleshow/131110765.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-16T17:24:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131111436,imgsize-82254.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['He couldn’t stop blushing': When Queen Elizabeth II smiled at Prince Harry, his reaction said everything]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131135251.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A heartwarming photograph of Queen Elizabeth II beaming with pride at Prince Harry's 2006 military graduation is captivating social media. The image highlights their tender bond, with experts noting the Queen's affection and Harry's youthful demeanor. This touching moment, showcasing a proud grandmother, resonates deeply with royal fans amidst more formal portrayals.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/he-couldnt-stop-blushing-when-queen-elizabeth-ii-smiled-at-prince-harry-his-reaction-said-everything/articleshow/131135251.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/he-couldnt-stop-blushing-when-queen-elizabeth-ii-smiled-at-prince-harry-his-reaction-said-everything/articleshow/131135251.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-16T17:05:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131135295,imgsize-380936.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Far-right agitators barred from entering UK ahead of anti-Islam activist Tommy Robinson rally]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131135746.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/starmer-government-bans-11-far-right-agitators-from-entering-uk-ahead-of-tommy-robinson-rally/articleshow/131135746.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/starmer-government-bans-11-far-right-agitators-from-entering-uk-ahead-of-tommy-robinson-rally/articleshow/131135746.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-16T16:29:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131135767,imgsize-77376.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ebola outbreak in DR Congo: Over 80 dead, 246 cases reported in Ituri province; health emergency declared]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131134865.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ebola-outbreak-in-dr-congo-over-80-dead-246-cases-reported-in-ituri-province-health-emergency-declared/articleshow/131134865.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ebola-outbreak-